The 24-year-old N'Koulou played in the middle of a three man defence as Marseille beat Metz 3-1 on Sunday.

A former target for Arsenal and Atletico Madrid, N'Koulou is well regarded around Europe. He is a product of the Kadji Sports Academy in Douala which also helped develop Samuel Eto'o and previously played for Monaco.

Napoli, Liverpool and Newcastle have also watched him in recent seasons. 

